315
00:16:37,159 --> 00:16:38,440
Okay. I'll come by tomorrow.

316
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:40,840
Thirty million!

317
00:16:44,279 --> 00:16:45,519
Come on, let's move.

318
00:16:46,399 --> 00:16:47,600
