319
00:16:49,200 --> 00:16:49,840
No.

320
00:17:30,880 --> 00:17:31,359
Ming!

321
00:17:31,839 --> 00:17:32,279
Ming!

322
00:17:35,079 --> 00:17:35,480
Ouyang.

323
00:17:36,319 --> 00:17:37,240
You're here early.

324
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:40,440
Dressed like a biker and all,

325
00:17:40,440 --> 00:17:41,400
