330
00:17:51,559 --> 00:17:52,319
This place is like a treasure bowl,

331
00:17:52,319 --> 00:17:52,759
right?

332
00:17:53,039 --> 00:17:54,720
You know feng shui, huh?

333
00:17:55,160 --> 00:17:56,039
A treasure bowl means

334
