342
00:18:11,880 --> 00:18:12,990
(Lindao Nursing Home)

343
00:18:13,079 --> 00:18:13,920
Easy now. Easy.

344
00:18:14,119 --> 00:18:15,599
Mr. Wang's improved a lot this week.

345
00:18:15,920 --> 00:18:16,279
Watch your step.

346
00:18:16,440 --> 00:18:17,240
Careful here.

347
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:18,200
Be careful.

348
00:18:18,720 --> 00:18:19,519
Really impressive.

349
00:18:19,759 --> 00:18:20,240
Great job.

350
00:18:21,079 --> 00:18:22,480
That's right.

351
00:18:23,079 --> 00:18:23,440
Good.

352
00:18:23,559 --> 00:18:24,119
Excuse me.

353
00:18:24,200 --> 00:18:25,640
We're looking for Chen Zinuo.

354
00:18:26,000 --> 00:18:26,799
And you are?

355
00:18:26,839 --> 00:18:27,440
Friends of hers.

356
00:18:54,480 --> 00:18:55,480
Okay, this way.

357
00:19:00,640 --> 00:19:00,960
