360
00:19:03,279 --> 00:19:04,079
They're living well.

361
00:19:05,920 --> 00:19:06,440
She's over there.

362
00:19:06,680 --> 00:19:07,599
Have a seat here.

363
00:19:07,599 --> 00:19:08,079
Thank you.

364
00:19:08,240 --> 00:19:08,519
Sure.

365
00:19:22,359 --> 00:19:23,359
I got one too!

366
00:19:23,680 --> 00:19:24,680
I'm on a roll!

367
00:19:41,480 --> 00:19:41,960
Your turn.

368
00:19:42,119 --> 00:19:42,640
What's with you today?

369
00:19:42,640 --> 00:19:44,359
What's taking you so long?

370
00:19:44,880 --> 00:19:45,519
Hurry up!

371
00:19:45,519 --> 00:19:46,440
No, no, no.

372
00:19:46,599 --> 00:19:47,279
Discard that one.

373
00:19:47,279 --> 00:19:48,640
You'll have three winning tiles.

374
00:19:50,519 --> 00:19:50,799
Right.

375
00:19:50,799 --> 00:19:51,279
Seven Dots.

376
00:19:51,839 --> 00:19:52,279
Seven Dots.

377
00:19:54,440 --> 00:19:54,799
Mahjong!

378
00:19:55,559 --> 00:19:56,119
Self-draw!

379
00:19:56,200 --> 00:19:57,279
You must've seen my tiles!

380
00:19:57,400 --> 00:19:58,160
No, no.

381
00:19:59,000 --> 00:19:59,960
No way.

382
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:03,519
This hand doesn't count!

383
00:20:06,279 --> 00:20:06,720
Mr. Yu.

384
00:20:07,279 --> 00:20:07,880
I'm short on time.

385
00:20:08,559 --> 00:20:09,519
Just tell me what this is about.

386
00:20:10,200 --> 00:20:11,559
Ms. Chen, here's the thing.

387
00:20:11,640 --> 00:20:14,079
I'm living in your old house now.

388
00:20:14,119 --> 00:20:15,839
The villa you used to own.

389
00:20:16,279 --> 00:20:18,440
The property manager said
there are unpaid fees.

390
00:20:18,720 --> 00:20:19,240
I know.

391
00:20:19,799 --> 00:20:20,559
After what happened

392
00:20:20,960 --> 00:20:21,960
to my family

393
00:20:22,039 --> 00:20:22,920
the court seized the house

394
00:20:23,119 --> 00:20:23,839
and auctioned it off.

395
00:20:24,079 --> 00:20:25,359
So all outstanding debts of the house

396
00:20:25,519 --> 00:20:26,480
are assumed by the buyer.

397
00:20:26,680 --> 00:20:27,519
So those debts

398
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:29,279
have nothing to do with me

399
00:20:29,279 --> 00:20:29,920
or my family.

400
00:20:31,960 --> 00:20:32,799
That's an actual rule?

401
00:20:33,680 --> 00:20:34,079
Sir,

402
00:20:34,599 --> 00:20:35,839
how long has that cello girl

403
00:20:36,160 --> 00:20:37,000
been volunteering here?

404
00:20:37,799 --> 00:20:39,039
What cello girl?

405
00:20:39,319 --> 00:20:40,400
Show some respect.

406
00:20:40,759 --> 00:20:41,759
Her name is Nuo.

407
00:20:42,519 --> 00:20:43,000
Nuo.

408
00:20:43,400 --> 00:20:44,319
How long has Nuo

409
00:20:44,319 --> 00:20:44,920
been volunteering here?

410
00:20:45,519 --> 00:20:46,279
Seven or eight years.

411
00:20:46,519 --> 00:20:46,920
Seven Dots.

412
00:20:47,400 --> 00:20:48,240
Nuo

413
00:20:48,240 --> 00:20:49,759
comes from a good family

414
00:20:50,079 --> 00:20:51,519
Everyone here adores her.

415
00:20:51,799 --> 00:20:52,799
The line of admirers she's got

416
00:20:52,799 --> 00:20:53,559
