417
00:20:53,599 --> 00:20:54,680
to Italy.

418
00:20:55,079 --> 00:20:56,759
Looking at yourself.

419
00:20:56,920 --> 00:20:58,200
What chance do you think you have?

420
00:21:00,160 --> 00:21:00,519
Mr. Yu.

421
00:21:01,079 --> 00:21:01,839
Is there anything else?

422
00:21:02,079 --> 00:21:02,880
Just one thing.

423
00:21:03,440 --> 00:21:04,559
I get the feeling

424
00:21:04,559 --> 00:21:07,039
your family moved out in a hurry.

425
00:21:07,240 --> 00:21:07,680
So...

426
00:21:08,119 --> 00:21:09,279
did you happen to leave

427
00:21:09,279 --> 00:21:10,359
anything behind?

428
00:21:10,880 --> 00:21:11,680
Or maybe...

429
00:21:11,720 --> 00:21:12,839
while you were living there,

430
00:21:12,839 --> 00:21:14,359
did you ever come across

431
00:21:14,680 --> 00:21:15,559
anything unusual?

432
00:21:24,359 --> 00:21:24,880
Nuo.

433
00:21:25,440 --> 00:21:25,839
Nuo.

434
00:21:26,319 --> 00:21:27,240
Aunt You is looking for you.

435
00:21:27,440 --> 00:21:28,720
She wants to hear Hungarian Rhapsody.

436
00:21:39,319 --> 00:21:39,759
Like this.

437
00:21:39,759 --> 00:21:40,920
The paint goes on more evenly.

438
00:21:45,039 --> 00:21:45,519
Give it a try.

439
00:22:17,359 --> 00:22:19,200
Wenwen, who did you draw?

440
00:22:20,319 --> 00:22:20,920
My grandma.

441
00:22:21,799 --> 00:22:23,160
What's grandma doing?

442
00:22:23,599 --> 00:22:24,920
She's trying to bite my dad to death.

443
00:22:28,440 --> 00:22:29,680
Everyone, back to your seats.

444
00:22:30,319 --> 00:22:31,119
Work on your own drawings.

445
00:22:44,880 --> 00:22:45,240
Wenwen.

446
00:22:46,400 --> 00:22:46,920
Wenwen.

447
00:22:48,000 --> 00:22:48,839
Look at my markers.

448
00:22:49,160 --> 00:22:49,920
There are 120 colors.

449
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:51,079
I've got several blues

450
00:22:51,480 --> 00:22:52,359
for drawing the sky.

451
00:22:52,799 --> 00:22:53,680
And several yellows

452
00:22:54,119 --> 00:22:54,880
for the ground.

453
00:22:55,440 --> 00:22:55,880
Next time,

454
00:22:56,119 --> 00:22:56,799
we can share them.

455
00:22:57,079 --> 00:22:58,160
So what if you have 120 colors?

456
00:22:58,279 --> 00:22:59,519
You still failed art.

457
00:22:59,720 --> 00:23:00,960
Your drawings are as ugly as you are.

458
00:23:02,440 --> 00:23:03,119
What's ugly about them?

459
00:23:03,519 --> 00:23:04,160
They're okay.

460
00:23:04,839 --> 00:23:05,319
But I think

461
00:23:05,319 --> 00:23:06,160
yours looks better.

462
00:23:06,680 --> 00:23:07,559
All those big sharp teeth.

463
00:23:07,880 --> 00:23:08,599
It's different.

464
00:23:09,119 --> 00:23:10,400
I heard Ms. Cai

465
00:23:10,400 --> 00:23:11,279
calling your mom.

466
00:23:11,680 --> 00:23:12,559
She said you're really talented.

467
00:23:14,799 --> 00:23:15,440
Can you teach me?

468
00:23:16,279 --> 00:23:16,839
Please teach me.

469
00:23:16,839 --> 00:23:17,759
Would you stop bugging me?

470
00:23:38,480 --> 00:23:39,000
She's bleeding!

471
00:23:41,039 --> 00:23:41,599
She's bleeding!

472
00:23:43,799 --> 00:23:44,519
What do we do?

473
00:23:45,160 --> 00:23:46,160
She's bleeding!

474
00:23:46,799 --> 00:23:47,200
Wenwen!

475
00:23:47,480 --> 00:23:48,400
Your head!

476
00:23:53,079 --> 00:23:55,000
She's bleeding!

477
00:23:58,839 --> 00:23:59,559
It doesn't hurt.

478
00:24:00,119 --> 00:24:01,160
What's going on?

479
00:24:01,599 --> 00:24:02,319
What are you all looking at?

480
00:24:03,039 --> 00:24:03,359
Let me see.

481
00:24:05,440 --> 00:24:06,680
Wenwen, what happened?

482
00:24:08,519 --> 00:24:09,920
Are you hurt?

483
00:24:10,839 --> 00:24:12,119
What happened, Wu Xiaoxuan?

484
00:24:15,200 --> 00:24:15,559
It's okay.

485
00:24:15,880 --> 00:24:17,200
It's okay.

486
00:24:20,319 --> 00:24:20,799
Don't be scared.

487
00:24:21,279 --> 00:24:22,480
Hello, 120?

488
00:24:23,000 --> 00:24:24,160
This is Yingsi School.

489
00:24:24,960 --> 00:24:26,160
One of our students is injured.

490
00:24:26,200 --> 00:24:26,680
It's serious.

491
00:24:40,160 --> 00:24:41,680
♪I'm gonna work hard and make money♪

492
00:24:42,680 --> 00:24:43,119
Ms. Zhang.

493
00:24:46,440 --> 00:24:46,880
Where is she?

494
00:24:57,519 --> 00:24:58,079
Taxi!

495
00:25:14,440 --> 00:25:14,880
Does it hurt?

496
00:25:15,920 --> 00:25:16,440
Does it still hurt?

497
00:25:17,400 --> 00:25:18,079
I'm okay.

498
00:25:18,920 --> 00:25:19,599
Feeling better?

499
00:25:21,720 --> 00:25:22,839
Good. You're okay.

500
00:25:47,359 --> 00:25:48,279
Where to?

501
00:25:49,480 --> 00:25:50,960
39 Xinchen Road.

502
00:25:50,960 --> 00:25:51,160
Okay.

503
00:26:01,680 --> 00:26:02,519
People's Hospital?

504
00:26:03,200 --> 00:26:03,799
What happened?

505
00:26:04,200 --> 00:26:04,960
She got hurt?

506
00:26:05,160 --> 00:26:05,839
Where?

507
00:26:06,160 --> 00:26:07,559
Her head? Her head!

508
00:26:07,720 --> 00:26:08,480
Okay, okay.

509
00:26:08,680 --> 00:26:09,319
People's Hospital.

510
00:26:09,400 --> 00:26:10,319
I got it.

511
00:26:11,519 --> 00:26:12,000
She's fine.

512
00:26:12,440 --> 00:26:13,920
Kids heal quickly.

513
00:26:14,319 --> 00:26:15,160
Even if it scars,

514
00:26:15,599 --> 00:26:16,359
it'll be very faint.

515
00:26:17,039 --> 00:26:18,880
There are laser treatments now.

516
00:26:19,079 --> 00:26:19,680
So don't worry.

517
00:26:19,920 --> 00:26:21,640
She'll be as beautiful as ever.

518
00:26:23,200 --> 00:26:24,079
Thank you, Dr. Li.

519
00:26:26,519 --> 00:26:27,960
What on earth were you doing?

520
00:26:28,000 --> 00:26:28,880
Look what happened.

521
00:26:29,200 --> 00:26:30,359
I take care of her

522
00:26:30,400 --> 00:26:31,039
