523
00:26:31,240 --> 00:26:31,799
And you?

524
00:26:32,240 --> 00:26:32,799
You?

525
00:26:33,440 --> 00:26:34,359
What's it got to do with you?

526
00:26:34,640 --> 00:26:35,200
Can you watch her

527
00:26:35,200 --> 00:26:35,960
