528
00:26:36,039 --> 00:26:36,799
What do you mean

529
00:26:36,839 --> 00:26:37,480
it has nothing to do with you?

530
00:26:37,920 --> 00:26:39,400
Look at all those stitches.

531
00:26:39,559 --> 00:26:40,519
Nothing to do with you?

532
00:26:40,640 --> 00:26:41,599
So this is my fault?

533
00:26:41,799 --> 00:26:42,920
It wasn't his fault!

534
00:26:43,559 --> 00:26:44,519
I can't tell you what to do,

535
00:26:44,680 --> 00:26:45,359
but he's my son.

536
00:26:45,440 --> 00:26:46,359
I can still talk to my own son!

537
00:26:46,960 --> 00:26:47,839
Say something!

538
00:26:48,200 --> 00:26:48,640
Someone's arguing over there.

539
00:26:48,640 --> 00:26:49,119
Come on.

540
00:26:49,559 --> 00:26:51,119
This is a hospital, a public place.

541
00:26:51,119 --> 00:26:51,880
How embarrassing!

542
00:26:51,960 --> 00:26:53,640
This embarrasses the family. Let's go.

543
00:26:53,640 --> 00:26:54,160
What are you doing?

544
00:26:54,519 --> 00:26:54,960
Let go.

545
00:26:55,319 --> 00:26:55,799
Go ahead.

546
00:26:55,960 --> 00:26:56,680
Beat him to death.

547
00:26:57,119 --> 00:26:57,759
Go on.

548
00:26:57,960 --> 00:26:59,240
One is dead already. Just kill another.

549
00:27:00,359 --> 00:27:00,799
I'm sorry.

550
00:27:00,920 --> 00:27:01,920
Yu Ming, why are you apologizing?

551
00:27:02,000 --> 00:27:02,839
Who hasn't been hurt?

552
00:27:02,920 --> 00:27:03,839
Haven't you?

553
00:27:03,960 --> 00:27:05,039
And didn't it hurt?

554
00:27:05,119 --> 00:27:05,880
Your son was hurt.

555
00:27:05,880 --> 00:27:06,799
Do you even know where?

556
00:27:06,799 --> 00:27:07,680
Do you?

557
00:27:09,119 --> 00:27:09,839
His brother gave him that.

558
00:27:10,000 --> 00:27:11,319
Every time you scolded him,
he cut himself.

559
00:27:11,440 --> 00:27:12,079
Didn't that hurt?

560
00:27:12,160 --> 00:27:13,039
You're his mother.

561
00:27:13,079 --> 00:27:13,960
You think he wasn't hurt?

562
00:27:13,960 --> 00:27:15,119
Answer me!

563
00:27:15,200 --> 00:27:16,039
Kill him!

564
00:27:16,160 --> 00:27:17,319
Don't give me that.

565
00:27:17,319 --> 00:27:18,519
What kind of nonsense is that?

566
00:27:18,720 --> 00:27:19,359
Listen.

567
00:27:19,759 --> 00:27:20,319
Let go.

568
00:27:20,680 --> 00:27:21,039
Get out!

569
00:27:21,160 --> 00:27:21,799
That's enough.

570
00:27:22,000 --> 00:27:22,839
He's my son.

571
00:27:23,039 --> 00:27:23,799
I can discipline him.

572
00:27:23,920 --> 00:27:25,119
Mind your own child.

573
00:27:25,119 --> 00:27:25,920
What did your son do?

574
00:27:26,079 --> 00:27:27,119
Get over here.

575
00:27:27,960 --> 00:27:29,400
You can't afford 100 yuan

576
00:27:29,400 --> 00:27:30,000
for a set of markers.

577
00:27:30,039 --> 00:27:30,960
Yet one mistake outside,

578
00:27:31,039 --> 00:27:32,119
